(1, 'admin_page', 'O:8:"stdClass":26:{s:3:"nid";s:1:"1";s:3:"vid";s:1:"1";s:4:"type";s:10:"admin_page";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:7:"created";s:10:"1213225307";s:7:"changed";s:10:"1215625615";s:7:"comment";s:1:"0";s:7:"promote";s:1:"0";s:6:"sticky";s:1:"0";s:18:"revision_timestamp";s:10:"1215625615";s:5:"title";s:18:"Why Scholars Sites";s:4:"body";s:1831:"<div class="accordion-front">\r\n<h3 class="first"> It''s incredibly easy to set up a site</h3>\r\n<p>\r\nCreate an account on the Scholars'' Web Sites Project and instantly get a powerful, dynamic and elegant website (for free). Ready for you to enter and manage your content, organize your work, and publish news, announcements, presentations, class materials, and much more.\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>Manage and display your publications</h3>\r\n<p>\r\nEasily add <em>any kind of publication</em> using predefined web forms, or by importing them from a formatted file (such as EndNote, RIS, bibTex). You can also <strong>export</strong> your publication to different formats; select a variety of bibliographic styles (original, CSE, APA, IEEE, etc.)\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>Easy to create and manage your web site content</h3>\r\n<p>\r\nYou can create and update all your web site content using super simple predefined forms and an easy to use WYSIWYG editor. Enter and update your publications, your correct contact information, presentations, class materials, announcements.\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>Categorize the content of your web site</h3>\r\n<p>\r\nEvery piece of content in your site (publications, presentations, static pages) can be categorized using modern ''tags'' using an extremly easy interface. Your colleagues all over the world can instantly find your work.\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>Select from a variety of themes, or use your own</h3>\r\n<p>\r\nPick the look and feel of your site by choosing a theme during the registration. Switching to another theme at any time. Change font and background colors on the fly. You can even have a custom professionally design theme imported.\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>And more!</h3>\r\n<p>\r\nProvide <strong>RSS feeds</strong> for your visitors to subscribe to; different widgets to enable for your site; post notices about possible collaborative projects.\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n";s:6:"teaser";s:375:"<div class="accordion-front">\r\n<h3 class="first"> It''s incredibly easy to set up a site</h3>\r\n<p>\r\nCreate an account on the Scholars'' Web Sites Project and instantly get a powerful, dynamic and elegant website (for free). Ready for you to enter and manage your content, organize your work, and publish news, announcements, presentations, class materials, and much more.\r\n</p>";s:3:"log";s:0:"";s:6:"format";s:1:"3";s:3:"uid";s:1:"1";s:4:"name";s:12:"scholaradmin";s:7:"picture";s:0:"";s:4:"data";s:24:"a:1:{s:7:"contact";i:0;}";s:4:"path";s:18:"why-scholars-sites";s:4:"tags";N;s:22:"last_comment_timestamp";s:10:"1213225307";s:17:"last_comment_name";N;s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:8:"taxonomy";a:0:{}s:5:"files";a:0:{}}'),
